<li><a href="http://www.bodyglove.com/" target="newwindow"><img src="images/logos/logo_body_glove.jpg" width="150" height="44" hspace="3" align="left" />Body Glove</a> The Ultimate Watersports brand known for wetsuits, PFDs, boardshorts, swimwear, snorkeling equipment, and mobile phone and technology accessories.
